  </td> </tr>
</table>
</p>

@BGRND{{}}
<p>
Unlike the nominaliser <a href="grammar-no-nominaliser.html">@HI{{no}}</a>, @HI{{@EM{{koto}}}} tends to indicate
something to which the speaker does not feel very close.
</p>

